<TEXT>
<P>
JERUSALEM -- Clashes between Palestinians and Israeli police
erupted again on Thursday morning in East Jerusalem after a
Palestinian man was stabbed to death by an Israel Jew in the
previous day.
</P>
<P>
No casualties or injuries were reported so far.
(BC-Israel-Stabbing)
</P>
