<TEXT>
<P>
Jiang said that Morocco, a coastal country along the Atlantic
Ocean and the Mediterranean Sea, boasts rich mineral resources, a
long history, diligent people, beautiful scenery and an important
strategic location.
</P>
<P>
Under the leadership of Hassan II, Morocco has made marked
progress in safeguarding national independence, developing the
national economy and improving people's living standard, continued
Jiang.
</P>
<P>
Morocco, as an influential country in the Arab world and on the
African continent, is playing a special role in international and
regional affairs, which the Chinese side appreciates very much, he
stressed.
</P>
<P>
