</P>
<P>
The airport authority says it is unlikely to reopen the airport
today due to current weather conditions.
</P>
<P>
The snow started at around 06:00 this morning and led to
cancellation of a flight to Beijing scheduled to depart at
06:50. The airport shut down a short five minutes later.
</P>
<P>
The provincial expressway monitoring center announced that all
expressways have remained open in spite of heavy snow and no major
accidents have been reported. 
</P>
</TEXT>
