went back to school today.
</P>
<P>
Teachers and school authorities in Daniao Village in Yunnan's
Xuanwei City set up the temporary school made up of seven tents
beside the former campus yesterday.
</P>
<P>
Located in northeastern Yunnan, Xuanwei was jolted by an
earthquake measuring 5.1 on the Richter Scale on Tuesday. Two
primary schools in Daniao Village were severely damaged and
classes were suspended.
</P>
<P>
