spend 1.8 million yuan (about 217,000 U.S. dollars) to repair the
two schools and in the meantime school authorities are building
temporary tent classrooms as so to resume normal schooling as soon
as possible.
</P>
<P>
He said the teachers will try to make up the lessons missed by
conducting classes on the weekends.
</P>
<P>
Seismologists say some aftershocks are possible in Xuanwei in
the next few days. The local government is now distributing relief
materials and earthquake-related pamphlets to local residents.
