skating World Cup series with Li Jiajun taking the men's race and
Yang Yang (A) claiming the women's on Friday.
</P>
<P>
Li Jiajun, Nagano Olympic silver medalist in February, clocked
two minutes 28.80 seconds in the men's 1,500 meters event.
</P>
<P>
