Lord Cranborne.
</P>
<P>
The Daily Telegraph:
</P>
<P>
-- Prime Minister Tony Blair was on Thursday night striving to
rebuild his status as a senior European leader after Germany
further marginalized the government by officially backing moves to
end the national veto over European Union tax policy.
</P>
<P>
The Independent
</P>
<P>
