ceremony on TV. But for those who will go to the stadium, the
shuttle buses provided in the Park and Ride program would be a
better choice than driving their own cars," he added.
</P>
<P>
The Prime Minister said the Cabinet will take a ride in a
car-pool awaiting at Government House in order to save parking
space.
</P>
<P>
Bangkok has taken extraordinary measures to ease congestion
during the two-week Games. New highways link the main venues,
schools will be closed to keep parents off the roads,
traffic-choking roadworks will be closed and thousands of
traffic police are being deployed. 
