<HEADLINE> Overseas Investment up in Tianjin Development Zone </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TIANJIN, December 4 (Xinhua) -- Tianjin Development Zone has
approved 186 overseas-invested enterprises this year involving
1.23 billion U.S. dollars, an increase of 10 percent over the
year-ago period.
</P>
<P>
An official of the Tianjin Municipal government said that
structure of overseas investment in the zone is optimized. More
European and U.S. enterprises enter the zone with investment to
pillar industries.
</P>
